snippet.title: NU: Carnival - Bliss PV
snippet.description:
NU: Carnival - Bliss is a BL life simulation game for mobile. 

With fully-animated characters, NU: Carnival - Bliss offers an unparalleled immersive experience. A cast of amazing Japanese voice actors interpret each of the ten characters' unique appeal, every line brimming with emotion and personal charm. By taking part in limited-time events and festivals with the characters, players can enjoy intimate storylines with rich themes. Journey to a new world right now and drive your clan members wild!

========================================

🔹 App Store：https://apps.apple.com/app/id6470422741
🔹 Google Play：https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.darkwind.nucarnival
🔹 Instagram：https://www.instagram.com/nucarnival_bliss/
🔹 Twitter(X)：https://twitter.com/nucarnivalbliss

========================================
